DOMDocument.templateDescription: Advanced Presentation using MovieClips. Transitions, button and keyboard navigation pre-coded.

DOMTextRun.characters: TEMPLATE INSTRUCTIONS (Guide layer - not exported with SWF)

1. To add and remove slides, double-click the Slides movie clip. 2. To customize the settings, open the Actions panel and select the ActionScript layer. 3. To edit the header and footer, unlock the Background layer and edit the contents. 4. To run fullscreen, publish as a projector file and toggle fullscreen mode in the projector.
Navigate by using the keyboard arrows, button clicks, or spacebar.
